{"tid":442410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女人真係好難捉摸","createTime":"2017-10-20T15:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T02:55:26.000Z","uid":151948,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc16f6b0fc2548fadb9bc6f944b120806ec782f","tid":442410,"uid":151948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早兩日lunch搵左個女同事一齊食，本身想帶佢食間日本風木藝裝潢既港式餐廳，咁去到間野門口，我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女同事=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你覺得餐牌啲野食岩唔岩心水？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好似麻麻地，有冇其他選擇？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁...err...有既，附近有間餐廳係類似蕃X門食蕃茄湯底既...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：正喎，我想食好耐，果到既蕃茄湯好濃好足料，但要入到大埔食太遠喇，不了。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：好，就咁話。<br />\n<br />\n轉個頭行多2個街口就到左，終於坐定定叫餐喇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：嗱，我食開呢個特餐，A拼B拼C再揀湯底，蕃茄或者豬骨湯底...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：(諗左一陣）我想試下豬骨湯底...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你唔係話想食蕃茄湯好耐既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？行左咁耐先黎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：因為我見冇其他人叫豬骨底，咪想試下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喔喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇所謂啦，你喜歡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你真係好難捉摸啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等左一陣就上左餐。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我個豬骨湯無乜味，可唔可以&quot;不&quot;下你啲蕃茄湯試下？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：好喔，梗係得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後佢仲唔小心將啲蕃茄湯整污左自己條裙，又同我講佢食野成日都唔小心整親自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我遞上張紙巾比佢，點點頭微笑，然後默默進餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：女人真係好難捉摸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：有女肯同你個毒拎一齊食野汁到喇，仲想點"},{"pid":"e7d0287dcd2c510f9436e18260baf7df3747d10c","tid":442410,"uid":117821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"之後佢仲唔小心將啲蕃茄湯整污左自己條裙，又同我講佢<span style=\"color: red;\">食野成日都唔小心整親自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> 我遞上張紙巾比佢，點點頭微笑，然後默默進餐<br />\n<br />\n性暗示"},{"pid":"0a9030d8dce21336068589057cf5b245db11dab7","tid":442410,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T15:36:20.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"b397aec3cf485aa39f2c2bb72988f22282c75c99","tid":442410,"uid":151948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之後佢仲唔小心將啲蕃茄湯整污左自己條裙，又同我講佢<span style=\"color: red;\">食野成日都唔小心整親自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> 我遞上張紙巾比佢，點點頭微笑，然後默默進餐<br />\n<br />\n性暗示</blockquote><br />\n係現場感受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f053d3d307576909ea3021b0299186ff8db761","tid":442410,"uid":151948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T15:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1999</blockquote><br />\nsry for 1999 lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm